{"tid":1821974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓火山爆發  馬尼拉機場關閉","createTime":"2020-01-12T15:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T19:58:54.000Z","uid":209657,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8c1df3f590a74c3e0e37c8161582e465eaa145","tid":1821974,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e1b16b6fd5cc31c9c2bae4b.jpg/U3FVWksJl7Kor678_yhKh7MepbuAyLQVDxyCrw8cgq8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e1b16b6fd5cc31c9c2bae4b.jpg%2FU3FVWksJl7Kor678_yhKh7MepbuAyLQVDxyCrw8cgq8&h=4e9dfcfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n菲律賓塔阿爾火山（Taal）1月12日噴發，火山灰及濃煙衝上高空，當局擔心之後會有爆炸級的噴發，目前已經疏散數千人，馬尼拉國際機場則緊急停飛航班。<br />\n<br />\n在1月12日，塔阿爾火山不但發出巨響，也讓當地附近出現劇震，當局擔心在未來數日甚至數周內，火山也會有危險的爆發。事實上自去年3月起，塔阿爾火山已開始出現異常。該國政府部門稱，有需要疏散8000名附近居民。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，菲律賓火山地震研究所提升對塔阿爾火山的警戒級別，目前為第4級（最高第5級），意思為有迫在眉睫的爆發危機。<br />\n<br />\n馬尼拉的尼諾伊‧阿基諾國際機場（Manila Ninoy Aquino International Airport）之後指，受火山爆發出現的火山灰影響，機場已經臨時停飛所有往來航班。"},{"pid":"73fed3a6d0cf83aa18518f8749374f133d40b481","tid":1821974,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4j-dJ9xAn3Y&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4j-dJ9xAn3Y%26feature%3Demb_title&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=3dc1ac01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4j-dJ9xAn3Y&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e1b16b7fd5cc31c9c2bae4d.jpg/_zl3RtxOdZSbvRfGUpqIUMdWKUVTPQIo64Qox-uEKMc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e1b16b7fd5cc31c9c2bae4d.jpg%2F_zl3RtxOdZSbvRfGUpqIUMdWKUVTPQIo64Qox-uEKMc&h=dc96bc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/med